---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Polysciences — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Polysciences, a chemistry company with a 4,000+ product catalog since 1961, deployed a Formic robotic palletizing cell on a pay-for-productivity model — cutting OpEx 35% on day one."
  ogTitle="Polysciences — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="35% lower OpEx day one · 7 employees reassigned · 100% consistency"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/polysciences" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Polysciences
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Polysciences</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Chemical Manufacturing Leader Polysciences Partners With Formic to Introduce Automation To Their Production Process</h1>
    <p class="lede">Polysciences — a chemistry company with a 4,000+ product catalog since 1961 — deployed a Formic robotic palletizing cell on a pay-for-productivity model, cutting OpEx 35% on day one and reassigning seven employees to higher-value work.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/polysciences-hero.jpg" alt="Polysciences robotic palletizing cell" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Polysciences · robotic palletizing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1961</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Ownership</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Family-owned</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Chemical manufacturing</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Catalog</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">4,000+ products</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Model</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Pay-for-productivity</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Stacking 30-pound boxes <em>isn't chemistry</em>.</h2>
      <p>Operating since 1961 with a catalog of 4,000+ chemical products, Polysciences measures itself across five pillars: safety, quality, productivity, inventory, and delivery. Manually lifting and stacking 30-pound boxes across two shifts, six days a week on 10-hour shifts was a bottleneck. As a chemistry company, automation sat outside its core competency — and most vendors prioritized larger contracts over small-to-medium manufacturers.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>4,000+ product catalog since 1961</li>
        <li>30-lb boxes across 2 shifts, 10-hour days</li>
        <li>Vendors overlooked small-to-mid manufacturers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/polysciences-2.jpg" alt="Polysciences palletizing cell on the production floor" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Compact · no fencing</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic Stack robotic palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Formic Stack · OpEx model</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>A compact cell, <em>no fencing</em>.</h2>
      <p>Polysciences found Formic at a 2022 packaging trade show and deployed a robotic palletizing cell via Formic Stack on a Pay-for-Productivity (OpEx) model — $0 upfront capital, an hourly usage rate, and 24/7 maintenance included. Installation finished within two months of signing, and the cell runs compact, without safety fencing.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Formic Stack on a pay-for-productivity model</li>
        <li>$0 upfront capital, 24/7 maintenance included</li>
        <li>Installed within two months; compact, no fencing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"From a safety perspective, we now don't have someone that needs to stand there and lift heavy boxes and put them on a pallet during 10 hour shifts. As far as the quality, it's now 100% consistent."</blockquote>
      <cite>Sean Moore · Executive Director of Manufacturing, Polysciences</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Results</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">35% lower OpEx. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Day one.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">35%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">OpEx reduction, day one</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">7</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Employees reassigned</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">100%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Palletizing consistency</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Bring automation <em>to your process</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
